{"tid":2255143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"付國豪稱支持警察光明正大 出生內地光輝榮耀","createTime":"2020-10-23T10:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T05:08:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8e8ddbad37af74e601ce514b675d08fab51267","tid":2255143,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:13:38.000Z","msg":"自稱《環球網》記者的內地人付國豪去年8月在機場被示威者圍堵及襲擊，案件今續審，付國豪繼續出庭作供。他表示當日在場人士將寫有「我愛香港警察」句語的藍色上衣放到他的腿部，又高舉他的中國護照及身份證，他揚言這些都不會讓他感到被羞辱，皆因支持香港警察是光明正大的事，更自言生於內地天津市讓他感到光輝和榮耀。<br />\n<br />\n付又稱，在場人士將寫有「我愛香港警察」句語的藍色上衣放到其腿部以羞辱他，惟付認為對方「選錯了道具」。他自言，當時心想支持香港警察一事是光明正大的，而他當時所說的「我支持香港警察，你們可以打我了」一句，事後也被廣泛流傳。<br />\n<br />\n至於有人舉起付的中國護照及身份證，付今揚言：「我出生自中華人民共和國天津市，這是令我感到光輝和榮耀的東西。」故他認為此舉亦無法羞辱他。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/DBPWKHUREJDRXOH6CHNK2Y5XAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2FDBPWKHUREJDRXOH6CHNK2Y5XAE%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=aff1f299\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2FDBPWKHUREJDRXOH6CHNK2Y5XAE%2F&h=be5e2981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/DBPWKHUREJDRXOH6CHNK2Y5XAE/</a>"},{"pid":"42c1b12dfc7366ff3e7a0bf2d0237398d48541d8","tid":2255143,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f60ed381d2df08d94d5ea3fb55f5c3f2d6db07","tid":2255143,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:16:33.000Z","msg":"真定假？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bbs.creaders.net/upfile/images/20190815/20190815163957_96488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbs.creaders.net%2Fupfile%2Fimages%2F201908